name: Do Not Leave your Grave.
description:
This tomb has been standing for over a hundred years, the remains that were once here have already been taken to the ossuary, probably soon the government will destroy the tomb to make room for a new family, to keep tradition and memory alive , we have an obligation to care for the dead and their stories.

tomb found in the Cemiério Municipal do Aguá Verde-Curitiba/Br

2021 photogrammetry scan - Higor Casagrande
